!<br />\n<br />\n交通係問題。如果黨鐵又封，運100萬人過海靠巴士要超過一日。<br />\n<br />\n希望抛個磚，大家諗下點拆。"},{"pid":"61b2511008fcaea82e993b46043139360c994999","tid":1648794,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa6e3030800631896e3d927bd225b0c31f9d663","tid":1648794,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"和理非已經進化咗好多，警暴係唔會嚇怕佢地<br />\n<br />\nby 和理非屋企人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:43:01.000Z","msg":"和理非最大的武器就係冇武器，只要冇武器啲狗都咬唔入，出得嚟行預咗唔使保護，只要一個都不能少。"},{"pid":"597ba454bb1e7fea402c73d10247a9ff6c776327","tid":1648794,"uid":233193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"講真你人多，怕咩<br />\n<br />\n佢格硬黎，咪又可以博國際同情<br />\n<br />\n你要知道而家同前2個月比，外國關注勁左好多"},{"pid":"67691f4aaaf7298d02c40672a3dabc6afd808b05","tid":1648794,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"047471d2daa471d2830e2aab2ef24ec77d8476e8","tid":1648794,"uid":82699,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:14:02.000Z","msg":"有外國政要睇場<br />\n例如Ted Cruz"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"其實靠外國幫唔到幾多 人地最多同你打口水戰 唔通真係岀兵咩"},{"pid":"cb47d03f5588cb9d0476580695075af0eed0ac77","tid":1648794,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff63bb2a9e78c556767fae3e762501c73e73e53","tid":1648794,"uid":226466,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"其實我想問開花打游擊 除咗 引green object 出黎之外 有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大遊行反而可以俾傳媒做文章<br />\n<br />\n克警搞事又 sell 警暴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"用手足黎換黑警搞事？仲當係69呀 4個月啦 黑警搞事既野多到講唔曬啦 你估黑警仲介意傳媒點寫咩"},{"pid":"67eed976af6fcb2d98f31c0f3ce3566d7e8e3f7b","tid":1648794,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8ca7ae6aea054f25bd87f641e13332812f1aab3","tid":1648794,"uid":55449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"你當和你非殘廢